DAYMET climate tile index

Source: R/DAYMET_tiles-data.R
DAYMET_tiles.Rd

Polygon tile index for DAYMET climate data

Format

An sp SpatialPolygonsDataFrame with 404 features (rows) and 6 columns (columns):

Id

Tile Index Identification

Area

Area of each tile

XMin

Minimum x geographic decimal degree coordinate

XMax

Maximum x geographic decimal degree coordinate

YMin

Minimum y geographic decimal degree coordinate

yMax

Maximum y geographic decimal degree coordinate

Source

https://daymet.ornl.gov/
